<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  </head>

  <body style="font-family: sans-serif">
    <header>
      <div
        style="
          width: 100%;
          display: flex;
          height: 60px;
          background-color: #51a7f3;
          color: rgb(0, 0, 0);
          font-size: 18px;
          font-weight: bold;
          justify-content: center;
          align-items: center;
          text-align: center;
        "
      >
        <h style="position: relative">
          <i>Semicolon-Nostanding</i><br />
          비밀번호 찾기 메일입니다.
        </h>
      </div>
      <div
        style="
          background-color: white;
          width: 100%;
          height: 8px;
          margin-bottom: 30px;
        "
      ></div>
    </header>

    <section>
      <article
        style="
          display: flex;
          justify-content: center;
          width: 600px;
          max-width: 1500px;
          height: 350px;
          margin: 0 auto;
          margin-bottom: 70px;
          margin-top: 70px;
          display: flex;
          justify-content: flex-start;
          align-items: center;
          background-color: #f5f5f5;
          border: 1px solid #c4c4c4;
          border-radius: 10px;
        "
      >
        <div
          style="
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
          "
        >
          <div style="width: 600px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 5px">
            안녕하세요, <i>Semicolon-Nostanding</i> 입니다.
          </div>
          <div style="margin-bottom: 5px">
            저희 웹사이트를 방문해 주셔서 감사드립니다.
          </div>
          <div style="margin-bottom: 5px">
            요청하신 이메일 인증번호는 다음과 같습니다.
          </div>
          <div style="height: 40px"></div>
          <div
            style="
              display: flex;
              width: 400px;
              border: 2px solid #cccccc;
              border-radius: 10px;
              background-color: #ffffff;
              color: #ffce63;
              justify-content: center;
              text-align: center;
              align-items: center;
              font-size: 40px;
              font-weight: bold;
            "
          >
            <%=confirmNumber %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </section>
    <div style="width: 100%; height: 8px; background-color: white"></div>
    <footer
      style="
        font-size: 14px;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #51a7f3;
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
      "
    >
      <div style="margin-bottom: 10px">
        <a
          href="https://www.semicolon-nostanding.com"
          style="
            display: block;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-decoration: none;
          "
          ><img style="height: 70px" src="<%= nostandingLogo%>"
        /></a>
      </div>
      <p>Copyright ⓒ 2021-2022 weAct. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p style="font-size: 12px">
        본 메일은 발신전용입니다.<br />문의사항이 있으시다면
        <a
          href="https://github.com/codestates/Nostanding"
          style="text-decoration: none; color: #ffce63"
          >Semicolon-Nostanding Github</a
        >를 확인해주세요.
      </p>
      <br />
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
